      <button class="q-check-btn" onclick="check(20,'mcq','B')">Check</button>
      <div class="q-answer" id="q20-ans"><b><span class="ans-correct">✓ (B) 3.</span></b> The decision tree for 3 elements has $3! = 6$ leaves; height $\lceil \log_2 6 \rceil = 3$.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

